al Development</li>\r\n    <li>Secured Lending</li>\r\n</ul></div>','','filtered_html');
INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','services','0','20','20','und','0','<p>We work with you to ensure your business is protected and help reach solutions to your legal problems and requirements. Our advice will be clear, precise and practical to focus on the need of your business.</p>\r\n','Need to add a summary on this pages edit overlay. 140 words or less,required for google search rich snippet','filtered_html'),('node','services','0','21','21','und','0','<p>Nalders benefits from a highly experienced Wills, Probate and Trust department. Our services are available to all clients at any of our offices, or if requested we visit clients in hospitals, residential homes, their own homes, or elsewhere as appropriate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our relationship with our clients is of primary importance and we recognise that making a Will, applying for Probate or administering a Trust, can be a highly emotional and sensitive area of law. We therefore endeavour to make the process as stress free as possible. We offer all clients a personal, friendly and sympathetic approach assisting all our clients in planning and managing their affairs most effectively in a wide range of situations. Our team is experienced and skilled in working with the bereaved and the elderly.</p>\r\n','Need to add a summary on this pages edit overlay. 140 words or less,required for googles search rich snippet','filtered_html'),('node','office','0','22','22','und','0','With more than 225 years experience Nalders is committed to providing a quality legal service to each and every one of our clients.  Operating from eight offices Nalders provide a comprehensive range of local and national services.\r\n\r\nWe are able to offer helpful, efficient advice using up to date technology to ensure a cost effective and tailor-made service.  Nalders also offer a free initial consultation at all our offices. Please telephone your nearest office for an appointment.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Nalders your local solicitors in Camb