INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','services','0','23','23','und','0','We deal with a wide variety of civil dispute resolution both for commercial and private clients.\r\nWe have a positive cost-effective approach to solving matters and have specialist lawyers who get great results.','Need to add a summary on this pages edit overlay. 140 words or less,required for googles search rich snippet.','filtered_html'),('node','services','0','24','24','und','0','Nalders has more than 225 years local experience and operate 8 offices throughout Cornwall.  We pride ourselves on building strong, longstanding relationships with key institutions within the local community.  Our legal professionals have extensive experience and knowledge and can offer a comprehensive, tailor-made service to address all your legal issues.  We have held the Law Society LEXCEL accreditation, the legal quality mark, since 2004. Accredited firms are independently audited to ensure that they offer the highest standard of client care and practice management, so you can be sure you''re getting the best possible service.\r\n\r\n<div class = ".service_sub"> Delivery <div>\r\n\r\nWe want you to get access to the advice you need in the way you want it delivered and quickly whether that is face-to-face, through telephone conferences, email or post.\r\n\r\nPrices\r\nWe want to build good and longstanding relationships with Schools and we will work with you to achieve a pricing structure which fits your own particular needs or requirements.\r\n\r\n','Need to add a summary on this pages edit overlay. 140 words or less,required for googles search rich snippet','full_html'),('node','page','0','25','25','und','0','ent for and on behalf of Nalders LLP.  Nalders Solicitors is the trade name of\r\nNalders LLP and is a Limited Liability Partnership registered in England and Wales LLP\r\nNo. OC354499. We use the term partner to refer to a member of Nalders LLP. A list of the\r\nmembers may be inspected at ou